name: HIDING BEHIND A MASK
description:
we all in this world have a role, 
sometimes we follow our roles honestly 
and sometimes we also follow pretend roles, 
many people hide behind masks, 
maybe it's to cover up their shortcomings 
or want to look good in front of many people, 
it depends on their own choice, 
want to play an honest role or forever 
hide behind their masks
